item.title: about
item.description: This page is for listing all of my publications, projects, actualities and so on. I am G. bencsik, working as a Computer vision software engineer for an international automotive company. I graduaded both of my BSc. and MSc. in Pécs, University of Pécs, Hungary. My topic was sound DSP / adaptive filtering. It can be found under the projects/SyncEQ title. I will finish this site as soon as it possible with some basic stuff.
